##<a id="windows"></a> Install PKS CLI for Windows

1. On the command line, run the following command to download the Windows executable file: 
  <pre class="terminal">$ curl -LO http<span>s:</span>//storage.googleapis.com/pks-public/bin/windows/pks.exe</pre>
  
3. Move the executable into your `PATH`. 
